  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb - \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dab\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba 2\u0daf\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The period of admission of students for intermediate - middle grades in national schools ended on 2nd",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The first school term of the year 2022 will end on 07.09.2022, and the Ministry of Education says that after 02.09.2022, the Ministry of Education will not accept the applications for admission of students for intermediate grades in national schools.",
        "The ministry further said that the matters related to the appeals/applications that have been submitted will be considered according to the vacancies in the schools and the requests of the applicants and the relevant decisions will be given in the future."
      ],
